and for ancients, if you are keith then get on msn and talk to me. if you really arent lying, ur forgiven bro

I did it for him.

I actually do.[/quote]
No actually, you don’t.
So, he told you he bought a Domain firstly by accident than I told him it wasn’t a vps and wrote a Support ticket for him to get his money back, then directed him to a certain vps to buy (which he bought on the spot). Then I was setting it up for him (Because he let me have access) oh & that I added a lot of code\simple things to his server over the course of a day that he wanted me to add, because I felt like helping out. So, you don’t know what were talking about. Quit acting like you do, I’m not talking about is compiler\run.bat which is a easy

C:\Program Files (x86)\Java\jdk1.6.0_23\bin\javac.exe

fix. & that he had a todo list of like 15 things that he wanted me to add to his server as well.
